        <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">US Software Developer, DAFT Route</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Freelance developer from New York, remote clients in US and Europe.</p>
        <p class="text-green-700 font-medium">✓ DAFT application approved in 10 weeks. €4,500 investment was easy—already had savings. Kept US clients, added Dutch ones. Paying €140/month for Dutch insurance with dental supplement. Very happy with the move.</p>
      </div>

